# This list is way out of date and is a work in progress, it is recommended to read through the changelog instead.

# Default Keybinds
 * r - reset camera
 * y - place waypoint (only works while recording waypoints)
 * \ - hold to place block payload precisely
 * z - navigate to camera (experimental)
 * alt WASD - free camera movement, r to reset
 * alt click - open tile actions menu (contains logs)
 * hold shift to disable conveyor/conduit auto bridge
 * o - make all units invisible (including yourself)
 * shift o - toggle unit invisibility
 * ; - enable "build path", automatically moves to anything you place, rebuilds broken structures and assists teammates
 * ctrl f - find block

# Top Navigation Menu
 * Start recording waypoints - begin a new path, press y to add a waypoint
 * Also records item transfers and payload actions
 * Finish recording waypoints - finalizes the path
 * Follow recorded path - replay the recorded path
 * Stop following path - stop following path (note: assist and auto navigation are also considered paths)

# Settings
 * Display lighting
 * Send reactor warnings
 * Play a sound on reactor warning (sound can only play after a 10s break in reactor building)
 * Discord rich presence toggle
 * Weather opacity slider
 * Various others

# Misc Changes
 * Automatic conveyor/conduit bridging (genNAowl)
 * Autocomplete in chat for content icons (type : and then the first part of the name, use tab to complete)
 * Autocomplete in chat for player names (type @ and then start typing the name, press tab to complete)

